      • TASK_DONE_VALID_RATIO

        public static final double TASK_DONE_VALID_RATIO
        Number of done tasks to number of all tasks ratio. Used for validation estimated finish time - time can not be estimated after processing just one file. If actual ratio is higher than this one, finish time can be estimated.
